10. **Hyperspace Event Generator** _(if needed)_
11. **Quick-Reference Cheat Cards** _(as needed)_
12. **Safety & Ethics Card** _(as needed)_

***

## RULES LINKAGE

- **Era Lock:** Always active (10,538 BBY, Old Republic Sith Empire).
- **Safety Filters:** Always enforced, per v5.3.
- **Heat/Bond:** Weighted (probabilistic); not binary triggers.
- **Commander’s Discretion:** Only GM/core creator may alter safety/ethics/core systems; players may add compliant house rules.

***

